            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In the meantime, Bentley says it will have hybrid versions of each of its models on the market by 2023. The stated goal right now is to have all new Bentleys be battery-electric vehicles only by 2030. If that’s where the automaker is headed, why is it wasting resources playing with biofuel gasoline blends? It’s a good question.",
