            "text": "Bentley says in its press release it’s taking a “two-strand” strategy to make the company carbon neutral. Since internal combustion engines will conceivably be produced by Bentley for the next 9 years, using alternative fuels could help with attaining that goal. It almost sounds like the automaker is hedging its bet on electric vehicle technology, which if so is wise.",
